question: Question_01_(h)
statement:
The angle of a pendulum satisfies

$\displaystyle L\theta''(t) + c\theta'(t) + g\theta(t) = 0$

where \emph{L} is the length (which can be changed),
$\displaystyle c = 0.1 m/s$, and $g = 10
\text{m/s}^2$. Find the maximum frequency (in Hertz) of the pendulum
over all possible lengths \emph{L}.
